# Sample Collection API - Example Requests

## Authentication

### Register Agent
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

### Login Agent
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

## Sample Management (Protected Routes)
# Note: Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with the actual token from login response

### Get Samples for Agent
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/samples/AGENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

### Create New Sample
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/samples
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientName": "Jane Smith",
  "pickupAddress": "123 Main Street, City, State 12345",
  "scheduledDate": "2025-08-07",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "notes": "Handle with care - fragile samples",
  "agentId": "AGENT_ID"
}

###

### Mark Sample as Collected
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/samples/SAMPLE_ID/collect
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

### Report Sample Delay
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/samples/SAMPLE_ID/report-delay
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Traffic delay due to road construction"
}

###

## Health Check

### Server Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

